  <p>In order to provide you with with best meal schedule we can, Lattice needs some information that isn't normally included in a recipe. You might not be used to answering these sorts of questions about a recipe, so we've provided some examples below. Please contact us if something is still unclear or you have suggestions on how to improve this tutorial.</p>
